me.choco.locksecurity.utils.json

Interface JSONSerializable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LockedBlock, LSPlayer

    public interface JSONSerializable
    Any object that should be serialized as a JSON object should implement this class to contain write(JsonObject) and read(JsonObject) methods for simplicity and ease.
    Author:
    Parker Hawke - 2008Choco

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      boolean read(com.google.gson.JsonObject data)
      Read information from a JsonObject provided as a parameter.
      com.google.gson.JsonObject write(com.google.gson.JsonObject data)

    • Method Detail

      • write

        com.google.gson.JsonObject write(com.google.gson.JsonObject data)
        Write information to a JsonObject provided as a parameter. Any information that should be saved to file should be provided here
        Parameters:
        data - the JSON data object to modify
        Returns:
        the modified JSON data object

      • read

        boolean read(com.google.gson.JsonObject data)
        Read information from a JsonObject provided as a parameter. Any information that should be read from file to fields should be read from this data tag
        Parameters:
        data - the JSON data object to read
        Returns:
        true if the reading was successful
